68831b9c0b3f39b6851c04a","tid":410485,"uid":129739,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:58:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佛教唔係宗教 <br />\n係思想同哲學<br />\n<br />\n佛學世界無神無偶像<br />\n只有榜樣</blockquote><br />\n佛學同佛教係2回事"},{"pid":"1e3cbe8d4b1b0c0995f3628503601dc50d141d3f","tid":410485,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ISIS</blockquote><br />\n香港有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7f77d666f1fecc5842e7e228b077e64a161677","tid":410485,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:07:34.000Z","msg":"認真,好想了解下點解斯蘭教咁激進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c55e81e58f02cd5c16ba91aebba5f010e9e23b3","tid":410485,"uid":56311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:07:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佛教唔係宗教 <br />\n係思想同哲學<br />\n<br />\n佛學世界無神無偶像<br />\n只有榜樣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認同"},{"pid":"1fa3ccd62cf834d22c14320a33e46109676b1dc9","tid":410485,"uid":105031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真,好想了解下點解斯蘭教咁激進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中世紀基督徒仲激進，下下東征"},{"pid":"8e8f5fb4f9064ebf05ddd55a55921df49812a3fd","tid":410485,"uid":52477,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真,好想了解下點解斯蘭教咁激進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中世紀基督徒仲激進，下下東征</blockquote><br />\n伊斯蘭教本身唔激進 <br />\n某啲教義仲好過基督教<br />\n<br />\n你平日所見啲激進行為係佢地斷章取義既結果<br />\n佢地緩引左部份針時古時所寫下既古蘭經經文 <br />\n放係現今既世界用 <br />\n同時隻眼開隻眼閉唔理好多經文<br />\n<br />\n我印象最深刻係 &ldquo;殺一人如殺眾人 救一人如救眾人&rdquo; 基本上係無得neglect咁濟既經文黎<br />\n<br />\n而佢地分支派系間既內戰 都有好多經文禁止左 但唔知點解班友厚面皮到繼續開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以家既伊斯蘭教 係國際舞台上都係政治道具多 <br />\n而信奉伊斯蘭教義既信徒 我識既人都真係好人黎"},{"pid":"7dd4b92aa04fa6cd1c4e27f6fefc92df3aa048ab","tid":410485,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:21:10.000Z","msg":"香港有東正教會"},{"pid":"37c2c2a6cf2b3d97426e85fdfe775ac991c4d246","tid":410485,"uid":54046,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講下背景,無神論人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀書時期接觸過天主/基督教/佛教,冇特別感覺,佛教有時講D野幾有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n計劃用二至三年時間,親身接觸所有宗教(香港地）,對好多宗教有好多疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,都唔理解點會有人相信.<br />\n同一個教又有分支,好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />目前整理下同搵下教會,有冇巴絲可以介紹教會俾我去?<br />\n目前只知<br />\n-基督教(好多分支?）<br />\n-天主教<br />\n-佛教<br />\n-摩門教<br />\n-創價教<br />\n-回教<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基督教-基要派（恩福堂）<br />\n             福恩派（旺角浸信會）<br />\n-天主教-玫瑰堂<br />\n-佛教-漢傳（佛青）<br />\n           藏傳（吉祥香巴）<br />\n           南傳（太和寺<br />\n-摩門教-何文田個間（有靚女）<br />\n-創價教-九龍塘個間<br />\n-回教-尖沙咀清真寺"},{"pid":"e3ad5573b930dc0a1b839d091aa5a835c0e6faac","tid":410485,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:23:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佛教唔係宗教 <br />\n係思想同哲學<br />\n<br />\n佛學世界無神無偶像<br />\n只有榜樣</blockquote><br />\n佛教係宗教<br />\n佛學係哲學<br />\n就算佛教係佛學衍生出嚟都好 都係宗教<br />\n識少少唔好懶醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44048490924fa5a9f65f3c5d4488153df9bf569e","tid":410485,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講下背景,無神論人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀書時期接觸過天主/基督教/佛教,冇特別感覺,佛教有時講D野幾有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n計劃用二至三年時間,親身接觸所有宗